<section id="summary" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="summary">Summary</h2>
<ol type="1">
<li><strong>Import</strong> <code>java.util.Scanner</code>.</li>
<li><strong>Create</strong> <code>new Scanner(System.in)</code>.</li>
<li><strong>Use</strong> <code>nextInt()</code>, <code>nextDouble()</code>, or <code>nextLine()</code> based on the variable type.</li>
<li><strong>Watch out</strong> for the newline trap when switching from numbers to text!</li>
</ol>
<p>Happy Coding! üöÄ</p>


